{"tid":2303822,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白俄總統暗示或於憲法改革後辭職","createTime":"2020-11-28T09:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T09:39:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7af3aa228640ca4e0c164570f2ed6c9d68659832","tid":2303822,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562466-20201128.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562466-20201128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7ChvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=b9780dee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562466-20201128.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=048f24b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562466-20201128.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n白俄羅斯總統盧卡申科暗示，可能會辭去總統職務，但無透露時間表。<br />\n<br />\n盧卡申科認為，應該改革國家憲法，以減少總統的權力，在新憲法下，他不會擔任總統，但如果他現在移交權力，將會帶來麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n自從白俄羅斯在8月初舉行總統大選，並由盧卡申科勝選連任以來，全國連續多個月都有大規模抗議活動，認為盧卡申科操控選舉，要求他辭職。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫日前與盧卡申科會面，認為白俄應該推動憲法改革。不過白俄羅斯反對派認為，盧卡申科只是拖延時間。"},{"pid":"fa8cdf82b6abde5d6e77d65c8b6d9a43ef128077","tid":2303822,"uid":259901,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:08:39.000Z","msg":"林鄭表示會成立獨立檢討委員會"},{"pid":"81f615408e273046ec7b4b7b5bba6ac0dc627302","tid":2303822,"uid":231583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:08:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a098a03029a8a2c88e9ede85fa21e175aa45fabc","tid":2303822,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:11:39.000Z","msg":"學普京咁換位啫,唔會真係民主咗嘅"},{"pid":"c7f4deb21366d0ed6677427cc330689029e4d4cf","tid":2303822,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a098a03029a8a2c88e9ede85fa21e175aa45fabc","tid":2303822,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28